#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.model_selection.train_test_split.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.model\\_selection.train\\_test\\_split"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split:1 of
msgid "Split arrays or matrices into random train and test subsets"
msgstr "将数组或矩阵随机分割为训练集和测试集子集"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split:3 of
msgid ""
"Allowed inputs are lists, numpy arrays, scipy-sparse matrices or pandas "
"dataframes."
msgstr "允许的输入包括列表、numpy 数组、scipy 稀疏矩阵或 pandas DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split:6 of
msgid ""
"If float, should be between 0.0 and 1.0 and represent the proportion of "
"the dataset to include in the test split. If int, represents the absolute"
" number of test samples. If None, the value is set to the complement of "
"the train size. If ``train_size`` is also None, it will be set to 0.25."
msgstr ""
"如果为浮点数，应在 0.0 到 1.0 之间，并表示测试集中包含的数据比例。如果为"
"整数，则表示测试样本的绝对数量。如果为 None，则设置为训练集大小的补集。"
"如果 ``train_size`` 同时也为 None，则默认设为 0.25。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split:12 of
msgid ""
"If float, should be between 0.0 and 1.0 and represent the proportion of "
"the dataset to include in the train split. If int, represents the "
"absolute number of train samples. If None, the value is automatically set"
" to the complement of the test size."
msgstr ""
"如果为浮点数，应在 0.0 到 1.0 之间，并表示训练集中包含的数据比例。如果为"
"整数，则表示训练样本的绝对数量。如果为 None，则自动设置为测试集大小的补集"
"。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split:17 of
msgid ""
"If int, random_state is the seed used by the random number generator; If "
"RandomState instance, random_state is the random number generator; If "
"None, the random number generator is the RandomState instance used by "
"`np.random`."
msgstr ""
"如果为整数，random_state 是随机数生成器使用的种子；如果为 RandomState "
"实例，random_state 即为随机数生成器；如果为 None，则使用 `np.random` 所用"
"的 RandomState 实例作为随机数生成器。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split:22 of
msgid ""
"Whether or not to shuffle the data before splitting. If shuffle=False "
"then stratify must be None. CURRENTLY only shuffle=False is supported."
msgstr ""
"是否在分割前打乱数据。如果 shuffle=False，则 stratify 必须为 None。目前仅"
"支持 shuffle=False。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split:25 of
msgid ""
"If not None, data is split in a stratified fashion, using this as the "
"class labels."
msgstr "如果不为 None，则使用此参数作为类别标签以分层方式进行数据分割。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split:29 of
msgid "**splitting** -- List containing train-test split of inputs."
msgstr "**splitting** -- 包含输入数据训练集和测试集分割结果的列表。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.train_test_split of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

